sequenceDiagram
    participant App as Application
    participant CA as CacheAside
    participant C as Cache
    participant DS as DataSource

    Note over App, DS: Cache-Aside Read Path (Cache Hit)
    App->>CA: Get(ctx, "user:1")
    CA->>C: Get(ctx, "user:1")
    C-->>CA: []byte("data"), nil
    CA-->>App: []byte("data"), nil

    Note over App, DS: Cache-Aside Read Path (Cache Miss)
    App->>CA: Get(ctx, "user:2")
    CA->>C: Get(ctx, "user:2")
    C-->>CA: nil, nil
    CA->>DS: Load(ctx, "user:2")
    DS-->>CA: []byte("data"), nil
    CA->>C: Set(ctx, "user:2", data, 0)
    C-->>CA: nil
    CA-->>App: []byte("data"), nil

    Note over App, DS: Cache-Aside Write Path (Invalidation)
    App->>CA: Set(ctx, "user:1", newData, 0)
    CA->>DS: Store(ctx, "user:1", newData)
    DS-->>CA: nil
    CA->>C: Delete(ctx, "user:1")
    C-->>CA: nil
    CA-->>App: nil

    Note over App, DS: Cache-Aside Delete Path
    App->>CA: Delete(ctx, "user:1")
    CA->>DS: Remove(ctx, "user:1")
    DS-->>CA: nil
    CA->>C: Delete(ctx, "user:1")
    C-->>CA: nil
    CA-->>App: nil
